channel.title: Would anyone be interested
channel.description:
Hello, so i am comming to a big decision today, and want to know what the mopar community thinks about this, so im the owner of Mi-Webs webhosting as many of you know, and today, i was offered a deal for a VPS license to Resell vps's so im wondering, if anyone would be interested in this, if so let me know in a post,the Starting vps will be around $11.99 for a Windows Server and $10.99 for a Linux server, and eventually i will buy a root reseller where i can actually make VPS's myself. So let me know what you think, this is not a cheap decision as it will cost alot of money so i need to know if anyone is interested or not.
Thanks Mi-Webs owner
